{
  "title": "Charred Flaky Venezuelan Taco Shells Tacos",
  "description": "A post-workout meal featuring charred, flaky Venezuelan-style taco shells, topped with a tadka-inspired mixture of spices and protein-rich ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "Venezuelan",
